Package pkgMain

Class Controller

java.lang.Object
javafx.application.Application
pkgMain.Controller
public class Controller
extends javafx.application.Application
This is the main Controller for the whole application. In here will be the methods that will allow different View classes to talk to each other, as well as get information from the Model class
